Usage: ctd_save_histogram [-help] [-csv] -file <string> [-id <string>]

-help              # Prints out the command usage
-csv               # Save in CSV format. (bool, optional)
-file <string>     # File Name. (string, required)
-id <string>       # CTD Window ID, the default value is the id of active ctd
                   # window. (string, optional)